          "sequence": 9,
          "subtype": "message",
          "text": "## Summary\n\nI've found **6 concrete implementations** of the `AggregatedDiscoveryServiceServer` gRPC interface across the repositories:\n\n### envoyproxy/go-control-plane (1 implementation)\n- **`server`** (`pkg/server/v3/server.go`) \u2014 Production implementation with both `StreamAggregatedResources` and `DeltaAggregatedResources` methods\n\n### istio/istio (5 implementations)\n**Production:**\n1. **`DiscoveryServer`** (`pilot/pkg/xds/ads.go`) \u2014 Main Pilot xDS server with both streaming and delta methods\n2. **`XdsProxy`** (`pkg/istio-agent/xds_proxy.go`) \u2014 Istio agent xDS proxy implementing `StreamAggregatedResources`\n3. **`XdsProxy`** (`pkg/istio-agent/xds_proxy_delta.go`) \u2014 Istio agent xDS proxy implementing `DeltaAggregatedResources`\n\n**Test:**\n4. **`testAdscRunServer`** (`pkg/adsc/adsc_test.go`) \u2014 Test mock server with both methods\n5. **`mockDeltaXdsServer`** (`pkg/adsc/delta_test.go`) \u2014 Test mock server with both methods\n\n### emissary-ingress/emissary\nNo implementations found in this repository.\n\nResults written to `/workspace/implementors.json` \u2713",
